{
  "stem": "352.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it's like in, in a dream.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I do remember it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And all I know that one day, my mommy was crying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And, and my sister was crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And I started crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And my father did not come back home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And there was a roundup.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And we, he never came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we didn't know where he is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "This was right, I think, two or three months after the Germans came to, to Lodz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then-- this I don't remember, but my sister told me-- that my uncle Chaim, which was my, the brother of my mother, they went to [?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Bawuti, ?] this which was a marketplace in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he was among the first Jews that were hanged in the market.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "He was one of the first Jews that were hung.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "They were hung in Lodz, in the market.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "This my sister told me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Soon enough, there's something that I'm telling that I don't remember too much, but my sister related it to me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "People were scared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They started throwing out people from the better neighborhoods, like [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "Pyotrkovska ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "My, one of my aunts, she lived [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Zavotska ?].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And she came to live with us, [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Chochatola. ?] And things were happening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know that my mother was always crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Chochatola ?] was crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they say, what's going to happen to us?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then-- How old were you, Barbara?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in 1933, so I was around six years old, something like this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there are some things that I do remember and some that I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I guess we also have selective selective memory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But if it's frightful, I, I really don't remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I do remember that there was a lot of crying.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
